<lb n="0176a10" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0176005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】平安時代寫高山寺藏本，【乙】黃蘗板淨嚴等校訂加筆本，【丙】縮冊大藏經</note>大日經略攝念誦隨行法<note n="0176006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔亦名…譯〕五十八字－【甲】</note><note n="0176006" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: a-->（亦名…譯）五十八字【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><note place="inline">亦名五支略念誦要行法
<lb n="0176a11" ed="T"/><note n="0176007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【明】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0176007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一卷【大】，〔－〕【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0176007"><lem wit="【大】">一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0176a12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0176a13" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0176008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（開府…譯））四十六字＝（（唐北天竺三藏沙門大廣智不空奉詔譯））十六字【明】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0176008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（開府…譯）四十六字【大】，唐北天竺三藏沙門大廣智不空奉詔譯【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0176008" cb:word-count="46"><lem wit="【大】">開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅
<lb n="0176a14" ed="T"/>國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡
<lb n="0176a15" ed="T"/>大鑒正號大廣智大興善寺三藏
<lb n="0176a16" ed="T"/>沙門不空奉　詔譯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】">唐北天竺三藏沙門大廣智不空奉詔譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0176a17" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0176a1701"><l>稽首無礙智，<caesura/>密教意生子，</l>
<lb n="0176a18" ed="T"/><l>依彼蘇多羅，<caesura/>攝此隨行法。</l>
<lb n="0176a19" ed="T"/><l>真言行菩薩，<caesura/>先住平等誓，</l>
<lb n="0176a20" ed="T"/><l>語密身密俱，<caesura/>後作相應行。</l></lg>
<lb n="0176a21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0176a2101">三昧耶真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0176a22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0176a2201" cb:type="dharani"><note n="0176009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曩莫＝南麼【甲】＊</note><note n="0176009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曩莫【大】＊，南麼【甲】＊</note><app n="0176009"><lem wit="【大】">曩莫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南麼</rdg></app>三曼多勃馱<note n="0176010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">難唵＝南一唵二【明】，南唵【甲】，南一【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0176010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">難唵【大】，南一唵二【明】，南唵【甲】，南一【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0176010"><lem wit="【大】">難唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">南一唵二</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南唵</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">南一</rdg></app>阿三謎底哩<note place="inline">二合</note>三
<lb n="0176a23" ed="T"/>謎<note n="0176011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三〕－【甲】</note><note n="0176011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0176011"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">三</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>　<note n="0176012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三摩曳＝三摩耶【明】，三麼曳【甲】</note><note n="0176012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三摩曳【大】，三摩耶【明】，三麼曳【甲】</note><app n="0176012"><lem wit="【大】">三摩曳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">三摩耶</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">三麼曳</rdg></app><note n="0176013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（娑嚩…引））七字＝（（莎訶））二字【甲】</note><note n="0176013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（娑嚩…引）七字【大】，莎訶【甲】</note><app n="0176013" cb:word-count="7"><lem wit="【大】">娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline"><note n="0176014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＋（四）【明】</note><note n="0176014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】，引四【明】</note><app n="0176014"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">引四</rdg></app></note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莎訶</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0176a24" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0176a2401"><l>契謂<note n="0176015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">齊＝臍【明】【乙】【丙】＊</note><note n="0176015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">齊【大】＊，臍【明】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0176015"><lem wit="【大】">齊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】">臍</rdg></app>輪合，<caesura/>並建於二空，</l>
<lb n="0176a25" ed="T"/><l>五處頂肩心，<caesura/>最後加咽位。</l>
<lb n="0176a26" ed="T"/><l>次以<note n="0176016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不動聖＝無動尊【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0176016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不動聖【大】，無動尊【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0176016"><lem wit="【大】">不動聖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">無動尊</rdg></app>，<caesura/>辟障及除垢，</l>
<lb n="0176a27" ed="T"/><l>而能淨眾事，<caesura/>結護隨相應。</l></lg>
<lb n="0176a28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0176a2801">不動尊真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0176a29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0176a2901" cb:type="dharani"><app type="star" corresp="#0176009"><lem wit="【大】">曩莫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南麼</rdg></app>三曼多<note n="0176017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚩日囉二合＝伐折囉【甲】</note><note n="0176017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚩日囉二合【大】，伐折囉【甲】</note><app n="0176017"><lem wit="【大】">嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">伐折囉</rdg></app>𧹞<note n="0176018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引一〕－【甲】</note><note n="0176018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引一【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0176018"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>　戰拏<note n="0176019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩賀引＝摩訶【甲】</note><note n="0176019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩賀引【大】，摩訶【甲】</note><app n="0176019"><lem wit="【大】">摩賀
<pb n="0176b" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0857.0176b"/>
<lb n="0176b01" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">摩訶</rdg></app>嚧<note n="0176020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曬＝灑【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0176020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曬【大】，灑【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0176020"><lem wit="【大】">曬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">灑</rdg></app>拏<note n="0176021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二〕－【甲】</note><note n="0176021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0176021"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>　<note n="0176022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑頗＝薩頗【甲】，頗字下甲本夾註二字不明</note><note n="0176022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">娑頗【大】，薩頗【甲】，頗字下甲本夾註二字不明</note><app n="0176022"><lem wit="【大】">娑頗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">薩頗</rdg></app><note n="0176022" type="rest" place="foot">頗字下甲本夾註二字不明</note><note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0176023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吒野三＝吒耶【甲】</note><note n="0176023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吒野三【大】，吒耶【甲】</note><app n="0176023"><lem wit="【大】">吒野<note place="inline">三</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">吒耶</rdg></app>　吽怛羅<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0176b02" ed="T"/><note n="0176024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（吒半…五））九字＝（（唅引𤚥引））四字【甲】</note><note n="0176024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（吒半…五）九字【大】，唅引𤚥引【甲】</note><app n="0176024" cb:word-count="9"><lem wit="【大】">吒<note place="inline">半音呼</note><note place="inline">四</note>　憾<note place="inline">引</note>𤚥<note place="inline">五</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唅引𤚥引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0176b03" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0176b0301"><l>定空加地水，<caesura/>風火竪於心，</l>
<lb n="0176b04" ed="T"/><l>慧劍亦如<note n="0176025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝之【甲】</note><note n="0176025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是【大】，之【甲】</note><app n="0176025"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">之</rdg></app>，<caesura/>出鞘能成辦。</l>
<lb n="0176b05" ed="T"/><l>次<note n="0176026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">說＝以【甲】</note><note n="0176026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">說【大】，以【甲】</note><app n="0176026"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">以</rdg></app>如來鉤，<caesura/>用請於本尊，</l>
<lb n="0176b06" ed="T"/><l><note n="0176027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（一切眾聖主）∞（依本誓而來）【甲】，一＝上ィ【甲】</note><note n="0176027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（一切眾聖主）【大】∞（依本誓而來）【甲】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->一＝上ィ【甲】</note><app n="0176027"><lem wit="【大】">一切眾<note n="0176028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聖＝生【明】</note><note n="0176028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聖【大】，生【明】</note><app n="0176028"><lem wit="【大】">聖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">生</rdg></app>主</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">依本誓而來</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">上切眾聖主</rdg></app>，<caesura/><note n="0176029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（一切眾聖主）∞（依本誓而來）【甲】，依＝下ィ【甲】</note><note n="0176029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（依本誓而來）【大】∞（一切眾聖主）【甲】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->依＝下ィ【甲】</note><app n="0176029"><lem wit="【大】">依本誓而來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">一切眾聖主</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">下本誓而來</rdg></app>。</l></lg>
<lb n="0176b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0176b0701">如來鉤真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0176b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0176b0801" cb:type="dharani"><app type="star" corresp="#0176009"><lem wit="【大】">曩莫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南麼</rdg></app>三曼多勃馱<note n="0176030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">南＋（一）細註【明】</note><note n="0176030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">南【大】，南<note place="inline">一</note>【明】</note><app n="0176030"><lem wit="【大】">南</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">南<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>阿<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0176031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">薩嚩＝薩娑【甲】</note><note n="0176031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">薩嚩【大】，薩娑【甲】</note><app n="0176031"><lem wit="【大】">薩嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">薩娑</rdg></app>怛囉<note place="inline">二<note n="0176032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（二）【明】</note><note n="0176032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合【大】，合二【明】</note><app n="0176032"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">合二</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0176b09" ed="T"/>阿<note n="0176033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【甲】</note><note n="0176033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0176033"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>鉢<note n="0176034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝剌【甲】</note><note n="0176034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉【大】，剌【甲】</note><app n="0176034"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">剌</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>底<note n="0176035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＝喝【甲】</note><note n="0176035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賀【大】，喝【甲】</note><app n="0176035"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">喝</rdg></app><note n="0176036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多＋（三）細註【明】，多＝帝【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0176036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多【大】，多<note place="inline">三</note>【明】，帝【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0176036"><lem wit="【大】">多</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">多<note place="inline">三</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">帝</rdg></app>怛他<note n="0176037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">薩＝孽【明】【乙】【丙】，揭【甲】</note><note n="0176037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">薩【大】，孽【明】【乙】【丙】，揭【甲】</note><app n="0176037"><lem wit="【大】">薩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】">孽</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">揭</rdg></app>儻<note place="inline">引</note>矩奢
<lb n="0176b10" ed="T"/><note n="0176038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔四〕－【甲】</note><note n="0176038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">四【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0176038"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">四</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>　<note n="0176039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">冐地拶＝菩地遮【甲】</note><note n="0176039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">冒地拶【大】，菩地遮【甲】</note><app n="0176039"><lem wit="【大】">冒地拶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">菩地遮</rdg></app>哩耶<note place="inline">二合</note>波<note n="0176040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唎＝利【甲】</note><note n="0176040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唎【大】，利【甲】</note><app n="0176040"><lem wit="【大】">唎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">利</rdg></app>布囉<note place="inline">上<note n="0176041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔聲〕－【甲】</note><note n="0176041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聲【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0176041"><lem wit="【大】">聲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note>迦<note n="0176042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔半音〕－【甲】</note><note n="0176042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">半音【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0176042"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">半音</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0176b11" ed="T"/>娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note n="0176043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＋（五）【明】，〔引〕－【甲】</note><note n="0176043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】，引五【明】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0176043"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><note place="inline">引五</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0176b12" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0176b1201"><l>止觀內相叉，<caesura/>堅合智風竪，</l>
<lb n="0176b13" ed="T"/><l>纔屈於初分，<caesura/>餘輪狀若環。</l>
<lb n="0176b14" ed="T"/><l>聖天悲願力，<caesura/>隨請咸來降，</l>
<lb n="0176b15" ed="T"/><l>奉<note n="0176044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">現＝視【乙】</note><note n="0176044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">現【大】，視【乙】</note><app n="0176044"><lem wit="【大】">現</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">視</rdg></app>三昧耶，<caesura/>明契如前說。</l>
<lb n="0176b16" ed="T"/><l>既呈本誓已，<caesura/>發喜而無謬，</l>
<lb n="0176b17" ed="T"/><l>次當隨力分，<caesura/>供養表誠心，</l>
<lb n="0176b18" ed="T"/><l>閼伽香食燈，<caesura/>下至一花水，</l>
<lb n="0176b19" ed="T"/><l>或但心運想，<caesura/>殊勝最難量。</l>
<lb n="0176b20" ed="T"/><l>當以普通印，<caesura/>密語共加之，</l>
<lb n="0176b21" ed="T"/><l>有表無表俱，<caesura/>一<note n="0176045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時＝切【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0176045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時【大】，切【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0176045"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">切</rdg></app>皆成就。</l></lg>
<lb n="0176b22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0176b2201">普通真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0176b23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0176b2301" cb:type="dharani"><app type="star" corresp="#0176009"><lem wit="【大】">曩莫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南麼</rdg></app>三曼多勃馱南<note n="0176046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【甲】</note><note n="0176046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0176046"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>　薩嚩他欠<note n="0176047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">平聲＝平聲二【明】，〔平聲〕－【甲】</note><note n="0176047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">平聲【大】，平聲二【明】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0176047"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">平聲</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><note place="inline">平聲二</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0176048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嗢＝溫【明】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0176048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嗢【大】，溫【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0176048"><lem wit="【大】">嗢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】">溫</rdg></app>
<lb n="0176b24" ed="T"/>娜<note n="0176049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">孽二合＝薩【甲】</note><note n="0176049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">孽二合【大】，薩【甲】</note><app n="0176049"><lem wit="【大】">孽<note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">薩</rdg></app><note n="0176050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諦＋（三）細註【明】，諦＝底【甲】</note><note n="0176050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諦【大】，諦<note place="inline">三</note>【明】，底【甲】</note><app n="0176050"><lem wit="【大】">諦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">諦<note place="inline">三</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">底</rdg></app>薩頗<note n="0176051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【明】</note><note n="0176051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二合【大】，〔－〕【明】</note><app n="0176051"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>囉係<note n="0176052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔呬〕－【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0176052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呬【大】，〔－〕【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0176052"><lem wit="【大】">呬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0176053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">𤚥＋（四）細註【明】</note><note n="0176053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𤚥【大】，𤚥<note place="inline">四</note>【明】</note><app n="0176053"><lem wit="【大】">𤚥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">𤚥<note place="inline">四</note></rdg></app>伽伽那
<lb n="0176b25" ed="T"/>劍<note n="0176054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">平聲呼＝平聲【明】，〔平聲呼〕－【甲】</note><note n="0176054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">平聲呼【大】，平聲【明】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0176054"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">平聲呼</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><note place="inline">平聲</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0176055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（娑嚩…訶））六字＝（（娑嚩訶引五））五字【明】，（（莎訶））二字【甲】</note><note n="0176055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（娑嚩…訶）六字【大】，娑嚩訶引五【明】，莎訶【甲】</note><app n="0176055" cb:word-count="6"><lem wit="【大】">娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">娑嚩訶引五</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莎訶</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0176b26" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0176b2601"><l>禪智互相叉，<caesura/><app type="star" corresp="#0176015"><lem wit="【大】">齊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】">臍</rdg></app>輪頂上合，</l>
<lb n="0176b27" ed="T"/><l>運心普周遍，<caesura/>所念皆現前。</l>
<lb n="0176b28" ed="T"/><l>既施供養已，<caesura/>修常作持誦，</l>
<pb n="0176c" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0857.0176c"/>
<lb n="0176c01" ed="T"/><l>先擐金剛鎧，<caesura/>結護事相應。</l></lg>
<lb n="0176c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0176c0201">金剛甲冑真<note n="0176056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＋（曰）【明】</note><note n="0176056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言【大】，言曰【明】</note><app n="0176056"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">言曰</rdg></app>：</p>
<lb n="0176c03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0176c0301" cb:type="dharani"><app type="star" corresp="#0176009"><lem wit="【大】">曩莫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南麼</rdg></app>三曼多<note n="0176057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚩＋（日）【明】【乙】【丙】，嚩＝伐折【甲】</note><note n="0176057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚩【大】，嚩日【明】【乙】【丙】，伐折【甲】</note><app n="0176057"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】">嚩日</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">伐折</rdg></app>囉<note n="0176058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【甲】</note><note n="0176058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二合【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0176058"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0176059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">𧹞＋（一）細註【明】</note><note n="0176059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𧹞【大】，𧹞<note place="inline">一</note>【明】</note><app n="0176059"><lem wit="【大】">𧹞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">𧹞<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app><note n="0176060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚩日囉二合＝伐折囉【甲】</note><note n="0176060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚩日囉二合【大】，伐折囉【甲】</note><app n="0176060"><lem wit="【大】">嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">伐折囉</rdg></app>迦
<lb n="0176c04" ed="T"/>嚩<note n="0176061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者＝啫【明】</note><note n="0176061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者【大】，啫【明】</note><app n="0176061"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">啫</rdg></app><note n="0176062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吽＋（二）細註【明】</note><note n="0176062" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吽【大】，吽<note place="inline">二</note>【明】</note><app n="0176062"><lem wit="【大】">吽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">吽<note place="inline">二</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0176c05" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0176c0501"><l>先作虛心合，<caesura/>風輪糺持火，</l>
<lb n="0176c06" ed="T"/><l>大空依火本，<caesura/>遍觸後居心。</l>
<lb n="0176c07" ed="T"/><l>次結方隅界，<caesura/>如前不動尊，</l>
<lb n="0176c08" ed="T"/><l>左轉成辟除，<caesura/><note n="0176063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">右＝左【甲】</note><note n="0176063" resp="CBETA" type="mod">右【大】，左【甲】</note><app n="0176063"><lem wit="【大】">右</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">左</rdg></app>旋及上下，</l>
<lb n="0176c09" ed="T"/><l><note n="0176064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">備＝被【明】</note><note n="0176064" resp="CBETA" type="mod">備【大】，被【明】</note><app n="0176064"><lem wit="【大】">備</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">被</rdg></app>觸身支分，<caesura/>結護悉堅牢，</l>
<lb n="0176c10" ed="T"/><l><note n="0176065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">真言及本契＝真語母陀羅【甲】</note><note n="0176065" resp="CBETA" type="mod">真言及本契【大】，真語母陀羅【甲】</note><app n="0176065"><lem wit="【大】">真言及本契</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">真語母陀羅</rdg></app>，<caesura/><note n="0176066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如前＝前如【明】</note><note n="0176066" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如前【大】，前如【明】</note><app n="0176066"><lem wit="【大】">如前</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">前如</rdg></app>已分別。</l>
<lb n="0176c11" ed="T"/><l>既為嚴備訖，<caesura/>當示根本契，</l>
<lb n="0176c12" ed="T"/><l>還加五位處，<caesura/>七轉或<note n="0176067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">再＝載【明】</note><note n="0176067" resp="CBETA" type="mod">再【大】，載【明】</note><app n="0176067"><lem wit="【大】">再</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">載</rdg></app>三，</l>
<lb n="0176c13" ed="T"/><l>散印頂上開。<caesura/>半<note n="0176068" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">跏＝加【明】【甲】</note><note n="0176068" resp="CBETA" type="mod">跏【大】，加【明】【甲】</note><app n="0176068"><lem wit="【大】">跏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">加</rdg></app>正身意，</l>
<lb n="0176c14" ed="T"/><l>或作相應坐，<caesura/>隨<note n="0176069" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">方＝力【甲】</note><note n="0176069" resp="CBETA" type="mod">方【大】，力【甲】</note><app n="0176069"><lem wit="【大】">方</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">力</rdg></app>如教說。</l>
<pb n="0177a" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0857.0177a"/>
<lb n="0177a01" ed="T"/><l>正面住身前，<caesura/><note n="0177001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">覩＝現【明】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0177001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">覩【大】，現【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0177001"><lem wit="【大】">覩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】">現</rdg></app>一圓明像，</l>
<lb n="0177a02" ed="T"/><l>清淨無<note n="0177002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">瑕玷＝假照【甲】</note><note n="0177002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">瑕玷【大】，假照【甲】</note><app n="0177002"><lem wit="【大】">瑕玷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">假照</rdg></app>，<caesura/>猶如滿月輪，</l>
<lb n="0177a03" ed="T"/><l>中有本尊形，<caesura/><note n="0177003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如＝妙【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0177003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如【大】，妙【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0177003"><lem wit="【大】">如</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">妙</rdg></app>色超三界，</l>
<lb n="0177a04" ed="T"/><l><note n="0177004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妙縠＝絹縠【甲】</note><note n="0177004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妙縠【大】，絹縠【甲】</note><app n="0177004"><lem wit="【大】">妙縠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">絹縠</rdg></app>嚴身服，<caesura/>寶冠紺髮垂，</l>
<lb n="0177a05" ed="T"/><l>寂然三摩地，<caesura/>輝焰過眾電，</l>
<lb n="0177a06" ed="T"/><l>猶如淨鏡內，<caesura/>幽邃現真容，</l>
<lb n="0177a07" ed="T"/><l>喜怒顯<note n="0177005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">顏＝形【甲】</note><note n="0177005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">顏【大】，形【甲】</note><app n="0177005"><lem wit="【大】">顏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">形</rdg></app>色，<caesura/>操持與願<note n="0177006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">等＝尊【甲】</note><note n="0177006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">等【大】，尊【甲】</note><app n="0177006"><lem wit="【大】">等</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">尊</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0177a08" ed="T"/><l>正受相應身，<caesura/>明了心無亂，</l>
<lb n="0177a09" ed="T"/><l><note n="0177007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無相淨法體＝無法相淨體【甲】</note><note n="0177007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無相淨法體【大】，無法相淨體【甲】</note><app n="0177007"><lem wit="【大】">無相淨法體</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">無法相淨體</rdg></app>，<caesura/>應願濟群生。</l>
<lb n="0177a10" ed="T"/><l>專注而念持，<caesura/><note n="0177008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">限數既終畢∞懈極後方已【明】【甲】</note><note n="0177008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">限數既終畢【大】∞懈極後方已【明】【甲】</note><app n="0177008"><lem wit="【大】">限數既終畢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">懈極後方已</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0177a11" ed="T"/><l><note n="0177009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">限數既終畢∞懈極後方已【明】【甲】</note><note n="0177009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">懈極後方已【大】∞限數既終畢【明】【甲】</note><app n="0177009"><lem wit="【大】">懈極後方已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">限數既終畢</rdg></app>。<caesura/>復結普通印，</l>
<lb n="0177a12" ed="T"/><l>虔誠啟願等，<caesura/><note n="0177010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慇＝殷【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0177010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慇【大】，殷【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0177010"><lem wit="【大】">慇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">殷</rdg></app>重<note n="0177011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">禮＝辭【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0177011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">禮【大】，辭【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0177011"><lem wit="【大】">禮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">辭</rdg></app>聖尊，</l>
<lb n="0177a13" ed="T"/><l>左轉無動<note n="0177012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">力＝刀ィ【甲】，刀【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0177012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">力【大】，刀【校異-甲】，刀【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0177012"><lem wit="【大】">力</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">刀</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">刀</rdg></app>，<caesura/>解前所結護，</l>
<lb n="0177a14" ed="T"/><l>還呈本尊契，<caesura/>頂上散開之。</l>
<lb n="0177a15" ed="T"/><note n="0177013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔心送…初〕二十字－【甲】</note><note n="0177013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（心送…初）二十字【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0177013" cb:word-count="20"><lem wit="【大】"><l>心送於聖天，<caesura/>五輪投地禮，</l>
<lb n="0177a16" ed="T"/><l>然起隨眾善，<caesura/>後會復如初，</l></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0177a17" ed="T"/><l>一時與二三，<caesura/>或四皆如此。</l>
<lb n="0177a18" ed="T"/><l>餘分旋繞塔，<caesura/>浴像<note n="0177014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">讚＝瀆【甲】，讀ィ【甲】，讀【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0177014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">讚【大】，瀆【甲】，讀【校異-甲】，讀【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0177014"><lem wit="【大】">讚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">瀆</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">讀</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">讀</rdg></app>方廣，</l>
<lb n="0177a19" ed="T"/><l>塗<note n="0177015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飾＝拭【明】【乙】【丙】，成【甲】</note><note n="0177015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飾【大】，拭【明】【乙】【丙】，成【甲】</note><app n="0177015"><lem wit="【大】">飾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】">拭</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">成</rdg></app>曼荼羅，<caesura/>布花讚佛德。</l>
<lb n="0177a20" ed="T"/><l>或復無雜念，<caesura/>專<note n="0177016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">注＝住【甲】</note><note n="0177016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">注【大】，住【甲】</note><app n="0177016"><lem wit="【大】">注</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">住</rdg></app>於等引，</l>
<lb n="0177a21" ed="T"/><l>以此淨三業，<caesura/>悉地速現前，</l>
<lb n="0177a22" ed="T"/><l>聖力所加持，<caesura/>行願相應故。</l>
<lb n="0177a23" ed="T"/><l>諸有樂修習，<caesura/>隨師而受學，</l>
<lb n="0177a24" ed="T"/><l>持明傳本教，<caesura/>無越三昧耶，</l>
<lb n="0177a25" ed="T"/><l>勤策無間斷，<caesura/>離蓋及熏醉，</l>
<lb n="0177a26" ed="T"/><l>順行於學處，<caesura/>悉地隨力<note n="0177017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">成＝威【明】</note><note n="0177017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">成【大】，威【明】</note><app n="0177017"><lem wit="【大】">成</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">威</rdg></app>。</l>
<lb n="0177a27" ed="T"/><l>我依大日教，<caesura/>略示瑜<note n="0177018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">伽＝祇【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0177018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">伽【大】，祇【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0177018"><lem wit="【大】">伽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">祇</rdg></app>行，</l>
<lb n="0177a28" ed="T"/><l>修證殊勝福，<caesura/>普潤諸有情。<note n="0177019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">情下乙本朱書右略述隨要常修法若欲具緣及觀種子當於阿闍黎所傳之二十四字</note></l></lg>
<lb n="0177a29" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><note n="0177020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（大日…法））十字＝（（大日瑜伽經））五字【甲】</note><note n="0177020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（大日…法）十字【大】，大日瑜伽經【甲】</note><app n="0177020" cb:word-count="10"><lem wit="【大】">大日經略攝念誦隨行法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">大日瑜伽經</rdg></app><note n="0177021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【明】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0177021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一卷【大】，〔－〕【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0177021"><lem wit="【大】">一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0177022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲本此下有普賢延命真言唵引薩嚩僧薩迦二合囉跛哩林馱達麼帝摩賀曩野跛<g ref="#CB13852"/>娑嚩二合引賀三十五字，乙本奧朱書云貞享甲子年九月七夕校之了，金剛乘資淨嚴四十六歲，元祿十五年十二月廿五日以和尚御本再校了尊敬</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>